BuzzVote,is,a,user,generated,social,polling,and,voting,platform,Users,can,create,or,vote,on,questions,and,share,questions,and,votes,socially,The,BuzzVote,API,provides,a,developer,interface,to,the,entire,platform,including,management,of,votes,questions,and,many,aspects,of,the,site,s,social,component,The,API,accepts,HTTP,POST,GET,calls,supports,SSL,and,returns,JSON,formatted,responses